{"tid":144662,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"關東 東京行程 求指教～","createTime":"2017-03-05T14:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T04:45:20.000Z","uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d85b7b6bc32b718cc5dfecc15d694024d35842f2","tid":144662,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"23／3 （四）成田機場 ＞ 酒店Check in ＞ 巢鴨地藏通商店街＞ 返酒店休息 ＞ 新宿一帶食玩 ＞ 歌舞技丁 ＞ 回酒店<br />\n<br />\n24／3（五） 早餐 ＞ 迪士尼 ＞ 涉谷區，代官山 ＞ 目黑川賞夜櫻 ＞ 返酒店<br />\n<br />\n25／3（六）鎌倉 江之島 ＞ 台場 ＞ 銀座 一帶 ＞ 回酒店<br />\n<br />\n26／3（日）富士山＞吉祥寺一帶行食玩 ＞井之頭恩賜公園賞櫻花＞食野返酒店<br />\n<br />\n27／3（一）築地 ＞ 秋葉原 淺草寺 阿美橫丁 ＞ 上野恩賜公園賞櫻 ＞ 隅田川公園 &gt; 晴空塔 &gt;晚飯<br />\n<br />\n28／3（二） Check out ＞ 機場Outlet ＞ 機場<br />\n<br />\n申：住池袋一帶 23號凌晨機<br />\n有無好西推仲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3e17ab5073d28b5cc929a65d0db0fb854aa404","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"竟然真係有人會去巢鴨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfcf9406fc92b1aa98ba53d628f53506d4c5840","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"day2 你去完迪士尼仲有冇咁多時間比你辣埋涉谷代宮山先？代宮山你唔係去 shopping 既話基本上冇野你行。"},{"pid":"9258730b75eca4c1a88ef59578b8d05fd5e4a203","tid":144662,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"認真，我覺得你要搞清楚啲時間觀念先<br />\nday2 樓上講左<br />\nday5 你係認真咁諗? 我諗你講富士山應該係指去河口湖睇<br />\n但day trip 基本上已經要晨早出去，跟住天未黑已經要返<br />\n仲可來有時間比你行埋吉祥寺個area呢"},{"pid":"7c34206f167f652d952ec9ee9e4d08ca1e250308","tid":144662,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，我覺得你要搞清楚啲時間觀念先<br />\nday2 樓上講左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">day5</span> 你係認真咁諗? 我諗你講富士山應該係指去河口湖睇<br />\n但day trip 基本上已經要晨早出去，跟住天未黑已經要返<br />\n仲可來有時間比你行埋吉祥寺個area呢</blockquote><br />\nday 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋江之島果日又係要用一日時間，所以之後嘅行程唔洗諗<br />\n簡單啲講，你太貪心"},{"pid":"0230ccd3ad1f0370db86e7ae733149e97b2b19fd","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，我覺得你要搞清楚啲時間觀念先<br />\nday2 樓上講左<br />\nday5 你係認真咁諗? 我諗你講富士山應該係指去河口湖睇<br />\n但day trip 基本上已經要晨早出去，跟住天未黑已經要返<br />\n仲可來有時間比你行埋吉祥寺個area呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日如果有 48 小時咁 plan 就唔錯。"},{"pid":"19f263f29208505260822515264999ae35c651c9","tid":144662,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然真係有人會去巢鴨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能帶埋老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b69c0269cf467e4b162841986d816a6d9dfbba","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然真係有人會去巢鴨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能帶埋老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五六十路既原宿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631ce9649a2075bf05a17571dc6efd25d5598ef6","tid":144662,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"睇怕要再Plan Plan 行程 😂😂"},{"pid":"5b0e59fdb5505c476dd050bf7ff1f6b3e22bd035","tid":144662,"uid":16530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"你住邊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左day 5應該跟到行程<br />\nday2,3,4你應該當左一日48小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70f2066ca0717d633e0988d956eb1255c8bb29","tid":144662,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢地d地理位置係邊<br />\n亂咁plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f734605cff464abc7688cc93726711df9efaec","tid":144662,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"唔爭在plan去埋大阪USJ即日來回喇<br />\n再整多日即日來回札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0c35f6c752cd580b13fe909df9b8ec781c110b","tid":144662,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"無話唔得既, 每個地方打個卡就走"},{"pid":"81adc562d3e0491dd45dabe34575ad544b5551d2","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇怕要再Plan Plan 行程 😂😂</blockquote><br />\n睇住 google map 黎 plan 啦，總之去近郊地方一定冇你大半日。"},{"pid":"dddfb7483c7dac600c13ab891b2649e2a47cd14c","tid":144662,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"day5 𠴱日如果你每個 location 可以搭的士既話應該唔太大問題，因為全部地點之間車程應該五至十分鐘內到，同埋而家的士短途起錶平左好多。銀座都可以放埋呢日，因為好近築地。"}]}